@startuml Workflow_APIGateway
title Workflow - API Gateway (Request Routing & JWT Verification)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FF
  BorderColor #4A6CF7
  FontSize 11
  ArrowColor #4A6CF7
  StartColor #4A6CF7
  EndColor #4A6CF7
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  DiamondBorderColor #FF9800
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFBE6
  BorderColor #FFC107
}
skinparam swimlane {
  BorderColor #4A6CF7
  TitleFontSize 12
  TitleFontStyle bold
}

|#EEF3FF| **HTTP Request** |
|#E8F5E9| **API Gateway** |
|#E3F2FD| **JwtService** |
|#FFF3E0| **TcpClientService** |
|#F3E5F5| **Target Microservice** |

start
|**HTTP Request**|
:Client gửi HTTP Request\nPOST/GET/PATCH/DELETE\n/api/v1/{service}/{endpoint};

|**API Gateway**|
:NestJS Router khớp controller;

fork
  :AuthGatewayController\n/api/v1/auth/*;
fork again
  :UsersGatewayController\n/api/v1/users/*;
fork again
  :AdminGatewayController\n/api/v1/admin/*;
fork again
  :SchedulerGatewayController\n/api/v1/scheduler/*;
fork again
  :CalendarGatewayController\n/api/v1/calendar/*;
fork again
  :AiGatewayController\n/api/v1/ai/*;
fork again
  :AnalyticsGatewayController\n/api/v1/analytics/*;
end fork

' ─── JWT VERIFICATION ────────────────────────────────────────────
:Endpoint yêu cầu Authentication?;
if (endpoint cần JWT?\n(tất cả trừ register/login/refresh\nforgot/reset password)) then (yes)
  :extractUserId(authHeader, jwtService);

  if (Header có 'Bearer '?) then (no)
    :Throw UnauthorizedException\n"No token provided";
    |**HTTP Request**|
    :401 Unauthorized;
    stop
  else (yes)
    :token = authHeader.substring(7);
    |**JwtService**|
    :jwtService.verify(token, { secret: JWT_SECRET });
    if (token không hợp lệ\nhoặc hết hạn?) then (yes)
      |**API Gateway**|
      :Throw UnauthorizedException\n"Invalid token";
      |**HTTP Request**|
      :401 Unauthorized;
      stop
    else (no)
      |**API Gateway**|
      :userId = payload.sub;
      :Tiếp tục xử lý request;
    end if
  end if
else (no — public endpoint)
  :Bỏ qua JWT verification;
end if

' ─── FORWARD TO MICROSERVICE ─────────────────────────────────────
:safeSend(tcpClient, serviceName, pattern, data);

|**TcpClientService**|
:Xác định TCP port theo serviceName:;
note right
  'user-service'      → TCP :3001
  'scheduler-service' → TCP :3002
  'calendar-service'  → TCP :3003
  'analytics-service' → TCP :3004
  'ai-service'        → TCP :3005
  'notification-svc'  → TCP :3006
  'queue-service'     → TCP :3007
end note

:tcpClient.send(pattern, data)\n(RxJS Observable → Promise);

|**Target Microservice**|
:@MessagePattern(pattern)\nHandler nhận payload;
:Xử lý business logic;
:Trả về kết quả;

|**TcpClientService**|
:Nhận response từ Observable;

|**API Gateway**|
if (Lỗi xảy ra?) then (yes)
  :Phân loại lỗi từ error.message:;
  if ("not found" in msg?) then (yes)
    :Throw BadRequestException(msg);
    |**HTTP Request**|
    :400 Bad Request;
  else if ("invalid" in msg?) then (yes)
    :Throw BadRequestException(msg);
    |**HTTP Request**|
    :400 Bad Request;
  else (unknown)
    :Throw InternalServerErrorException\n"Service error: {msg}";
    |**HTTP Request**|
    :500 Internal Server Error;
  end if
  stop
else (no)
  :Return response data;
  |**HTTP Request**|
  :200/201 OK + JSON body;
end if

' ─── SPECIAL: SCHEDULE GENERATE SYNC ────────────────────────────
|**API Gateway**|
note right
  ĐẶỆC BIỆT: Sau khi generateSchedule thành công:
  1. Gọi queue.schedule.list → lấy items
  2. Gọi calendar.schedule.replace → sync Calendar
  (syncSystemScheduleFromQueue helper)
end note

stop
@enduml
